OVERVIEW
=======
This is a package for publishing states from Linux joystick-type
devices on ach channels.  For basic library calls to read these
devices, see include/js.h.

Files
=====
* include/js.h,js.c - basic wrapper for polling a joystick (logitech gamepad)
* joyd.c - the joystick publisher

Usage
=====
Check program help text with:

    ./joyd -\?
